WEBVTT

00:02:30.600 --> 00:02:33.096
Ha megharịrị ọfụma,
m wee kutuo ume.

00:02:33.756 --> 00:02:36.400
E nwetụla m obere chiọma.

00:02:38.380 --> 00:02:41.800
Ya mere, n'otu akụkụ dị anya 
n'ọdịnihu nke Africa,

00:02:41.940 --> 00:02:45.756
Binti bụ ọkachamara mgbakọ na mwepụ
nke agbụrụ Himba

00:02:45.764 --> 00:02:48.560
Anabatala ya
n'ime mahadum dị n'ụwa ọzọ,

00:02:48.604 --> 00:02:50.240
o kpebiela na ya ga-aga.

00:02:50.720 --> 00:02:53.560
O bu ọbara
ndi agbụrụ ya n'akwara nke ya.

00:02:53.560 --> 00:02:57.656
eji nkuzi na amamiihe chọọ 
ya mma, ma n'elu akpụkpọ ahụ ya,

00:02:57.824 --> 00:02:59.960
Binti hapụrụ ụwa.